<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9200, 9300, 9400 Models Built After January 1, 1995 - POWER
        DISTRIBUTION &#38; GROUND SYSTEM - TROUBLESHOOTING - Testing 3 +1 Isolated Battery Magnetic Switch
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Testing 3 +1 Isolated Battery Magnetic Switch</title>
        <table id="t0805202" tblwidth="full-page" frame="all" numbered="no" view="reveal">
            <title>Test 2</title>
            <tgroup cols="7" align="center" charoff="50" char="c">
                <colspec colnum="1" colname="1" colwidth="0.59in"/>
                <colspec colnum="2" colname="2" colwidth="0.50in"/>
                <colspec colnum="3" colname="3" colwidth="1.80in"/>
                <colspec colnum="4" colname="4" colwidth="0.75in"/>
                <colspec colnum="5" colname="5" colwidth="0.75in"/>
                <colspec colnum="6" colname="6" colwidth="0.80in"/>
                <colspec colnum="7" colname="7" colwidth="1.80in" colsep="1"/>
                <spanspec namest="1" nameend="7" spanname="sqspan1-7"/>
                <thead valign="bottom">
                    <row>
                        <entry colspan="7" spanname="sqspan1-7" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">TESTING 3 +1 ISOLATED BATTERY MAGNETIC SWITCH</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody valign="top">
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold"></emph>
                                <emph type="bold">STEP</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold"></emph>
                                <emph type="bold">KEY</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">ACTION</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">TEST POINTS</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">YES-IN SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">NO-OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>At isolated magnetic switch, check voltage at terminal A to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>A to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>12&#177; 1.5 volts?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Perform Test 1
                                <hotlnk document="s08051_14.xml" xrefid="t0805201">Testing 3 +1 Battery System</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>At isolated magnetic switch, check voltage at terminal C to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>C to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>12&#177; 1.5 volts?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Repair cause of no or low voltage in black cable from cranking battery.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>3.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>At isolated magnetic switch, measure voltage between terminals C and circuit 11H.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>C to 11H.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>12&#177; 1.5 volts?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Repair open in ground circuit 11H.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>At isolated magnetic switch, measure voltage between terminals C and A.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>C to A.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>12&#177;1.5volts?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Replace the isolated magnetic switch.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>5.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>With engine running, measure voltage from terminal B to ground.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>B to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>6 to 8 volts?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Locate cause of no or low voltage in circuit 7 from alternator R terminal, then
                                repair.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="1">
                        <entry>
                            <para>6.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Disconnect red 3+1 cable from deep cycle battery. With engine running, at isolated
                                mag. switch, measure voltage from terminal A to gnd.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>A to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>12&#177;1.5volts?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>The3+1 system is working properly.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Replace the isolated magnetic switch.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
    </svcproc>
